# This package SHIPS every committed artifact reproduce.py reads, so `python reproduce.py`
# runs offline with no API key and no network. The raw census pool (~20 GB of deposited
# replication data, rebuilt from public DOIs via src/census_harvest.py) is local-only and
# must never be committed:
data/

# Local config (optional Dataverse API key for the corpus rebuild):
.env

# Python:
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.egg-info/
.venv/
